✨️ GIVEAWAY ALERT ✨️⁠
⁠
As seen on Taylor Swift (twice!), our Shimmer Chain has sold out twice in the past 3 months…and it’s back just in time for your Eras Tour looks!⁠
⁠
Want to win your very own Shimmer?⁠
⁠
The first person to visit our flagship at 505 Queen St W, Toronto, and say the code “I can still make the whole place shimmer” will walk away with a free Shimmer necklace!⁠ ⁠
⁠
Can’t make it in-store? No problem. Head to the link in our bio to enter the giveaway, and one additional winner will be chosen.⁠ ⁠
⁠
Whether you're lining up for merch or looking for last minute pieces to complete your Eras outfit, our flagship store is less than 20 minutes away from the action. Don’t wait—this piece has already sold out twice! ⁠
⁠
PLUS, enjoy up to 40% off in-store and online, including 15% off the Shimmer Chain!
